quran[8{c,v,t}:
7,44,"phir yeh jannat ke log dozakh walon se pukaar kar kahin ge,"" hum ne unn saaray wadon ko theek pa liya jo hamaray rab ne hum se kiye thay, kya tum ne bhi un wadon ko theek paaya jo tumahray rab ne kiye thay ?"" woh jawab den ge"" haan"" tab aik pukarnay wala un ke darmain pukare ga ke"" khuda ki laanat unn zaalmon par"
7,45,"jo Allah ke rastay se logon ko roktay aur usay terha karna chahtay thay aur akhirat ke munkir thay """
7,46,"un dono garohoon ke darmain aik oot haail hogi jis ki bulandiyon ( airaaf ) par kuch aur log hon ge yeh har aik ko is ke qiyafah se p_hchanin ge aur jannat walon se pukaar kar kahin ge ke"" salamti ho tum par"" yeh log jannat mein daakhil to nahi hue magar is ke umeed waar hunge"
7,47,"aur jab un ki nigehain dozakh walon ki taraf phrin gi to kahin ge,"" ae rab! hamein inn zalim logon mein shaamil nah kejio """
7,48,"phir yeh airaaf ke log dozakh ki chand barri barri shakhsiyation ko un ki alamton se pehchan kar pukaarain ge ke"" dekh liya tum ne, aaj nah tumahray jthe tumahray kisi kaam aeye aur nah woh saaz o samaan jin ko tum barri cheez samajte thay"
7,49,"aur kya yeh ahal jannat wohi log nahi hain jin ke mutaliq tum kasmain kha kha kar kehte thay ke inn ko to khuda panni rehmat mein se kuch bhi nah day ga? aaj unhi se kaha gaya ke daakhil ho jao jannat mein, tumahray liye nah khauf hai nah ranj """
7,50,"aur dozakh ke log jannat walon ko pukaarain ge ke kuch thora sa pani hum par daal do ya jo rizaq Allah ne tumhe diya hai usi mein se kuch pheink do woh jawab den ge ke"" Allah ne yeh dono cheeze unn munkareenhaq par haraam kar di hain"
7,51,"jinhon ne apne deen ko khail aur tafreeh bana liya tha aur jinhein duniya ki zindagi ne fraib mein mubtala kar rakha tha Allah farmata hai ke aaj hum bhi inhen isi terhan bhala den ge jis terhan woh iss din ki mulaqaat ko bhoolay rahay aur hamari aayton ka inkaar karte rahay """
